<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.3.3">
<l>maṉṉunara kaṉtaṉṉaic cūḻpōkiva ḷaitteṟintu</l>
<l>kaṉṉima kaḷirtammaik kavarntakaṭal vaṇṇaṉmalai</l>
<l>puṉṉaice runtiyoṭu puṉavēṅkaiyuṅ kōṅkunniṉṟu</l>
<l>poṉṉari mālaikaḷcūḻ poḻilmāliruñ cōlaiyatē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The mountain of the sea-hued One who, having gone to surround</l>
<l rend="indent">the resident of hell, seized and destroyed [him],</l>
<l rend="indent">carried off the virgin ladies,</l>
<l>that is Māliruñcōlai with groves surrounded by golden necklaces</l>
<l rend="indent">of Puṉṉai, Cerunti, upland Vēṅkai, and Kōṅku trees.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
